{"tid":1152438,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[RTHK] 新疆「再教育營」：被囚者的哭訴","createTime":"2019-05-13T03:30:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-13T07:15:39.000Z","uid":138409,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5a4788938e0c5ad255911cc5101da65c683be7cc","tid":1152438,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:30:24.000Z","msg":"全香港真係夠薑嘅媒體，真係一隻手數得曬<br />\n傳真社、RTHK、有線中國組<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （當然HKFP好似都幾好<br />\n-------------------------------<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.Pulse/videos/308033766807413/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHK.Pulse%2Fvideos%2F308033766807413%2F&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihEad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=c972b07b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHK.Pulse/videos/308033766807413/</a><br />\n中國近年大幅收緊宗教自由，打壓穆斯林，「伊斯蘭教中國化」的政策在全國各地推行。內地政府更以反恐及消滅極端主義為由，在新疆以「職業技能教育培訓」為名，大規模關押維吾爾族、哈薩克族及其他穆斯林。根據聯合國估計，目前被關押的人數已超過一百萬，當中包括著名的知識份子和精英。<br />\n<br />\n全新一集《脈搏》中文特輯將會帶大家走訪鄰近新疆的青海和寧夏，了解當地穆斯林的情況；以及跟新疆邊境接壤的哈薩克斯坦，採訪曾被囚禁的哈薩克人和正積極尋找被囚者的家屬。<br />\n<br />\n敬請留意：<br />\n<br />\n5月13日 (星期一)<br />\n港台電視31 (RTHK 31): 4 - 5pm<br />\n<br />\n6月2日 (星期日) *重播*<br />\n港台電視31 (RTHK 31): 5 - 6pm"},{"pid":"caa0e0aea2ff6f5651fe504c8ccf42f958155cb6","tid":1152438,"uid":138409,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">同場加映</span></span><br />\n[Vox] China's secret internment camps<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cMkHcZ5IwjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcMkHcZ5IwjU&d=JinSrGH%2FoctmVpTuEhnihEad0DqFW0GAicD%2BCHpJjC4%3D&h=11351ae9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cMkHcZ5IwjU</a>"},{"pid":"9ad338c761797ed5c3beadd02033859ea74b03e7","tid":1152438,"uid":165336,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"r